articleTitle: Positiv getestete Person war in Zug von Wien nach Graz unterwegs
articleTitleTranslated: The person who tested positive was traveling in Zug from Vienna to Graz
articleContent: Aufruf der AGES. Reise fand bereits vor einer Woche - am 17.  Februar statt.
articleContentTranslated: Call of AGES. The trip took place a week ago - on February 17th.
